# Cloudflare Pages custom headers.
# config.js carries the live Supabase project URL + anon key. It must never be
# served stale: a browser holding a cached config.js from before the 2026-06-30
# project cutover pointed the storefront at the old (archived) backend, which
# blanked the page. Force revalidation so a config change always takes effect.
/config.js
  Cache-Control: no-cache, must-revalidate
